image:WebIDECode.ApplicationSheet@XWebIDE.png
Welcome to the XWiki WebIDE, you can use it to create, edit and export XWiki Applications. This is the Master Page of the project, it contains meta-data such as the list of Folders and Pages which are part of the project.

__Get started__:
* **Edit a page** in your project by clicking on one of the edit buttons in the lefthand panel - you can edit the page in different modes for editing the content and metadata
* **Add a new folder** (also known as a Space) clicking the "add folder" button on the left
* **Add new page** when you need to create a new empty page in the selected folder
* **Add existing page** for times when you need to add a page which must be in a Space which is not part of your application's code
* **Export your project** as a XWiki .xar file which can be imported to other wikis or published on extensions.xwiki.org.

__Shortcuts for the wiki and object editors__:
* **Save & View** : Alt + S
* **Save & Continue** : Alt + Shift + S
* **Discard & View** : Alt + C

__Improve your IDE Experience__:
By installing the additional extensions you can improve the user interface of the XWiki WebIDE. To do so, use the [[Extension Manager>>XWiki.XWikiPreferences||queryString="editor=globaladmin&section=XWiki.AddExtensions"]].
* Install the [[Syntax Highlighting extension>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/Syntax+Highlighting+Application]]
* Install the [[Auto-Completion extension>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/AutoCompletion+Application]]

To learn about other features of the XWiki WebIDE, see the [[Online Documentation>>http://extensions.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Extension/XWebIDE+Application]] on xwiki.org.
